最佳解答: 
             1. 好久不見! 最近好嗎? 
我已收到修改PO, 但PO#1003357的價格應該是US$0.56而不是US$56, 麻煩請修改, 再次謝謝你的幫忙!! 
Hi, haven't heard from you for a while, how are you doing? 
I have received the modified PO, but the price of the PO #1003357 should be at USD0.56 rather than USD56. please kindly modify it and thank you for your help! 

2. 廠商表示沒有生產這個產品, 但有生產類似的產品, 請見參考附件的圖面, 請問是否可接受, 若可以, 我將提供報價給你 
We got the information from the supplier and they claim that they do not produce this product but they have some similar products. Please refer to the picture as attached and let us know if you will accept or not, if you accept it then I will send you the quotation soon. 

3. 我們急需要你的幫忙, 我們到現在還未收到11月份的貨款, 麻煩請盡快付款, 另外, 提醒你12月份的付款日期也即將到期, 很感激你的幫忙 
We need your help urgently that we have not received the payment of November, please arrange the payment as soon as possible. In addition to the payment of November, we have to remind the payment of December will be due soon. Your early reply is highly appreciated! 

4. 我們已經要求G&O重新 update price, 但今天尚未收到報價, 禮拜一將會提供給你 
We have requested the G&O to update the price again, but we still haven't received their reply. I will try my best to give you the update price next Monday! 

希望以上能幫到您! 




