 1. I haven't seen you for a long time. How are you now? 
   I've received the PO correction, but the price of PO#1003357 suppossed to be US$0.56 not US$56, Please help to correct it again, I'm appreciate your kindly help! 
2. Our manufacturers indicate that they didn't produce this product, but they have produced analogic products, please see attachment, if you could accept it, I'll offer the quotation for you. 
3. This is an urgent case, we need you do us a favor.Till now we didn't receive the payment of November.Please kindly pay for it ASAP.  Besides, the payment of December is due this month.I'm really appreciate for your assistant. 
4. We have requested G&O to update price, but we didn't receive the quotation yet, we'll offer the quotation on Monday.





