意見







 




新增意見











送出












 · 剛才不久























 1. 好久不見! 最近好嗎? 
我已收到修改PO, 但PO#1003357的價格應該是US$0.56而不是US$56, 麻煩請修改, 再次謝謝你的幫忙!! 
Hi, Hope everthing is well. 
I have received the revised PO, but the unit price on PO#1003357 should be USD 0.56, not USD 56, please revise it again. Thanks again for your help. 

2. 廠商表示沒有生產這個產品, 但有生產類似的產品, 請見參考附件的圖面, 請問是否可接受, 若可以, 我將提供報價給你 
The vendor informed they do not manufacture this product, but they do manufacture a similar product, please find attached drawing. Will this be acceptable? I will provide the quote if this is acceptable. 


3. 我們急需要你的幫忙, 我們到現在還未收到11月份的貨款, 麻煩請盡快付款, 另外, 提醒你12月份的付款日期也即將到期, 很感激你的幫忙 
We need your help urgently, we have not received payments for invoices due on November, please resolve this as soon as possible. For your information, invoices for December will be sending to you shortly, I will be much appriciated for your help.  

4. 我們已經要求G&O重新 update price, 但今天尚未收到報價, 禮拜一將會提供給你 
We have requested G&O to re-quote and update the price, but we have not received any feedback yet, I will provide the update pricing on Mondy (next Monday?)





