 1. 好久不見! 最近好嗎? 
我已收到修改PO, 但PO#1003357的價格應該是US$0.56而不是US$56, 麻煩請修改, 再次謝謝你的幫忙!! 

hi, how are you?  Haven't heard from you in a while. 
I have received the revised PO, but the price for PO#1003357 should be US$0.56 instead of US$56.  Please revise it.  Thanks again for your help. 

2. 廠商表示沒有生產這個產品, 但有生產類似的產品, 請見參考附件的圖面, 請問是否可接受, 若可以, 我將提供報價給你 
The manufacturer indicated that they do not make this product, but have other similar products.  Please refer to the acctached picture. 
If this is acceptable, please let me know and I will provide quotation to you. 


3. 我們急需要你的幫忙, 我們到現在還未收到11月份的貨款, 麻煩請盡快付款, 另外, 提醒你12月份的付款日期也即將到期, 很感激你的幫忙 
We are in need of your help on payments.  We have not received the payments for November, pls help us expedite.  Also, just a reminder that December payments will be dued soon.  Thanks again for your help. 

4. 我們已經要求G&O重新 update price, 但今天尚未收到報價, 禮拜一將會提供給你 
We have already requested the updated price from G & O but have not received it.  We will forward the quotation to you on Monday.





